## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="926ef-104">类的读写属性标记有<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementConfigurationAttribute>属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="926ef-104">The read-write properties of a class are marked with the <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementConfigurationAttribute> attribute.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="926ef-105">此外，每个读写属性可以是两种类型之一：<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementConfigurationType.Apply>或<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementConfigurationType.OnCommit>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="926ef-105">In addition, each read-write property can be one of two types: <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementConfigurationType.Apply> or <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementConfigurationType.OnCommit>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="926ef-106">如果类具有配置为 OnCommit 的读写属性，此类应具有与 ManagementCommit 属性标记的方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="926ef-106">If a class has read-write properties that are configured as OnCommit, the class should have a method that is marked with the ManagementCommit attribute.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="926ef-107">已设置所有 OnCommit 属性时，将调用关联的方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="926ef-107">The associated method will be called when all OnCommit properties have been set.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="926ef-108">标记的方法不是线程安全。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="926ef-108">The marked method is not thread safe.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="926ef-109">如果没有方法使用 ManagementCommit 属性标记，该类管理本身具有不更新已完成的任何指示的情况下配置更新。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="926ef-109">If no method is marked with the ManagementCommit attribute, the class manages the configuration updates by itself without any indication that the update has completed.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="926ef-110">用 ManagementCommit 属性标记的方法不带任何参数，它具有 void 返回类型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="926ef-110">The method marked with the ManagementCommit attribute does not take any parameters and it has a void return type.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
  
```csharp  
public class Process  
{  
    /// Key attribute marks a key property. Keys are not changeable.  
    /// Keys have to be unique information.  
    [ManagementKey]  
    public int Id   
    {  
        get {    }  
    }  
  
    /// ManagementConfiguration stands for read/write manageable  
    /// property from a read/write field.  
    [ManagementConfiguration]  
    public string UserDefinedString;  
  
    [ManagementCommit]  
    void SaveOnDevice();  
}  
```
